  "title": "Peripheralium",
  "description": "Library mod for all of my peripheral mods",
  "body": "<p><a title=\"Fabric Language Kotlin\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-language-kotlin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c1DH9VL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"171\" height=\"50\" /></a><a title=\"Fabric API\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"171\" height=\"50\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tooling library for making addon for CC:R and CC:T, used for my mods like <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/turtlematic\">Turtlematic</a> and <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/unlimitedperipheralworks\">UnlimitedPeripheralWorks</a>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Required dependencies (for Fabric):</p>\n<p>- <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-language-kotlin\">Fabric Kotlin</a></p>\n<p>- <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cc-tweaked\">CC: T</a></p>\n<p>- <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\">Forge Config API for Fabric</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Required dependencies (for Forge):</p>\n<p>- <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kotlin-for-forge\">Kotlin for Forge</a></p>\n<p>- <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cc-tweaked\">CC: T</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, you can join <a href=\"https://discord.gg/dYHKMQYRPp\">discord</a>.</p>",
